summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsGive BackMaybelline Super Stay Ink Crayon Lipstick glides on with no-hassle, for smudge-proof matte lip color that lasts all day. Features a built-in sharpener.
details: DetailsBenefitsDraw it on and bring it on, all day longLasting Ink technology glides across lips with no-hassle controlSmudge and transfer-resistantItem 2558100How To UseStep 1. Apply this long-lasting lipstick in the center of your upper lip and follow the contours of your mouth with the precise tip.Step 2. Use the wider side of the crayon to fill in lips, all in a swipe!IngredientsIsododecane, Polyethylene, Trimethylsiloxyphenyl Dimethicone, Isohexadecane, Dimethicone, Acrylates/Dimethicone Copolymer, Polypropylsilsesquioxane, Stearyl Heptanoate, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Hydrogenated Styrene/Methyl Styrene/Indene Copolymer, Alumina, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate, Limonene, Calcium Sodium Borosilicate, Aluminum Hydroxide, Polybutylene Terephthalate, Silica, Magnesium Silicate, Silica Silylate, Ethylene/Va Copolymer, Acrylates Copolymer, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Benzyl Benzoate, Tin Oxide, Benzyl Alcohol, Citronellol, Linalool, Geraniol, Disodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Tocopherol, Parfum / Fragrance. May Contain: CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, CI 45410 / Red 28 Lake, CI 15850 / Red 7, CI 45380 / Red 22 Lake, Mica, CI 15985 / Yellow 6 Lake, CI 19140 / Yellow 5 Lake, CI 77163 / Bismuth Oxychloride, CI 17200 / Red 33 Lake, CI 42090 / Blue 1 Lake, CI 15850 / Red 6, CI 75470 / Carmine.
how_to_use: Step 1. Apply this long-lasting lipstick in the center of your upper lip and follow the contours of your mouth with the precise tip.Step 2. Use the wider side of the crayon to fill in lips, all in a swipe!

reviews.headline: Great long-wear color!
reviews.comments: I love the color.  It is spotless on my lips; stays long and moisturizes them.  It does not leave any mess on utensils or glasses as well.

reviews.headline: no.
reviews.comments: It's not worth it, it's not long wearing, and it doesn't glide on smoothly even after making sure my lips are moisturized (coming from someone who uses matte liquid lipsticks)

reviews.headline: Love this Crayon
reviews.comments: I love this lip Crayon.   So many great colors.  Great quality and fairly affordable

reviews.headline: Great product
reviews.comments: Lipstick stayed on all day and the color didn't fade.  It was a bit drying, so I used a gloss over it.  Will be on my list of go-to products.

reviews.headline: So so
reviews.comments: Easy use, but eyes look dirty like after long party night

reviews.headline: Not a fan
reviews.comments: It lasts and the color is good but it tastes like alcohol to me. Glad it wasn't expensive.

reviews.headline: Great
reviews.comments: I really enjoy this. It stays on and is creamy. I use a gloss over it for extra moisture but so far this matte crayon lip pen has been the best matte lipstick I have used by far!

reviews.headline: Not worth the price tag
reviews.comments:
Great pigment! And has some nice looking shades. I did not like it though. I chose the Seek Adventure shade thinking it was a light/pale pink, which it is, but it has a strong undertone of purple and I really don't like that. No way to know without buying it either.
It goes on smooth, is buildable, and the edges stay for a while but the inside closer to the inside of your mouth disappears in minutes. It smudges, it clumps as it dries, and is unflattering after not long at all, and clearly does NOT last like it says it should. Not happy with it.
Probably won't recommend.

reviews.headline: I wear this everyday
reviews.comments: I love this color on me. I will buy additional colors in the future. Very nice

reviews.headline: lipstick and liner in one
reviews.comments: I learned to color my lips entirely with lip liner to encourage lipstick to stay longer, because I'm old apparently, but with this I don't need anything extra if I don't want to. I would like a few more colors, and faster setting, but this is honestly my dream product for lazy days.

reviews.headline: Great,
reviews.comments: Great, stay put for a while,  and a good price,ðŸ¤—

reviews.headline: Bad smell
reviews.comments: Smelled rancid. Returned.

reviews.headline: Smelled bad
reviews.comments: I love the Ink Crayon.  I have bought these from other places and they are great.  I bought this from Ulta and the smell is horrible. Smells like old chemicals. the color was off and didn't look like it should.  Very disappointed.

reviews.headline: 5 stars
reviews.comments: Love it... have many colors

reviews.headline: Lasts a long time, smells nice, good quality
reviews.comments: This is a long lasting lip liner, lasts all day and doesn't really transfer at all. Smells good and comes with a sharpener at the end. It's good quality

reviews.headline: My favorite
reviews.comments: I snatch this up every chance in case they stop making it, i love it!!

reviews.headline: I do love these lip crayons
reviews.comments: This color Make it Happen a true berry, just didn't look good on me, it leans to the pink side, I need more of a purple blue berry.  It is a beautiful color just not for my skin tone.  I will pass it to one of my granddaughters or nieces. For reference blue eyes, fair to light with yellow undertones.

reviews.headline: Be Bold Be You
reviews.comments: I am reviwing the beet color, Be Bold, Be You. This is a nice pinky red for me. Normally I stick to blue reds and avoid most pinky reds but this one worked out. I really like this color. I think the Superstay crayon is really worth the price. These make excellent lip liners for other brands lipsticks as well as staying put on my lips more than most other lipsticks I own, even lipsticks that are 4x this price. The colors I own don't dry my lips or stain them.

reviews.headline: Easily accessible, beautiful color!
reviews.comments: Such a beautiful color! easy to carry around if needed, blends beautifully for perfect lippie looks!

reviews.headline: Love this lip stain
reviews.comments: Great product it last from the moment I put it on at 6 in the morning til after the gym of 2 hour classes , food shopping, and eating!  Til the late afternoon noon

faceoff_positive.comments: Excellent colors and it is Superstay! Put on an initial coat and let dry completely once you put on. It will still be slippery and will transfer color while still wet so if you drink or touch your lips to anything it will smudge. Of course with any longwear lipsticks if you eat something greasy or use lip gloss it will not be superstay! You need to know how to use product! I love it and get plenty compliments!!
faceoff_positive.headline: Rich pigmented lip color. Superstay!

faceoff_negative.comments: Doesn't stay at all!!! Very misleading product. Applied for the first time and it wipes right off. Doesn't stay on for any length of time. Forget it if you plan on having a meal, or drinking anything. Maybelline needs to work on color stay formulas. Very, very disappointed! Do not recommend this product at all!
faceoff_negative.headline: Super Sad
